    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/boys_on_top/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">礼士路西岛秀俊</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-10"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-10 13:02:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5692392_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  因为一直游走在各种讽刺、吐槽、含沙射影的文字中，所以很久没有认真地写过一篇评论了。本年度第一篇，也很可能是最后一篇严肃的评论，想好好地写给李娟，她是今年我最喜欢的作家，没有之一。而且难能可贵的是，今年看过她的三本书——《冬牧场》《我的阿勒泰》和《夏牧场》，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5692392/#comments">(16回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">51有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5692392_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5692392_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










